title: Spider-Man Season One (2012) (GN) (Digital)
description:
Marvel: Season One is a new initiative aimed at attracting new comic fans from the millions of people who know Marvel characters from movies, television, and video games. Each Season One volume is a stand-alone tale designed to give readers a complete story, modernizing the seminal origins of these super-hero icons while also offering new revelations for long-time fans. This is the real Marvel Universe that current fans know and love, updated for a new generation.

    SPIDER-MAN: SEASON ONE PREMIERE HC: The greatest origin story of all time, 
                           retold for a new generation.

        COLLECTING: Spider -Man : Season One 1-5, Avenging Spider -Man 1
